    "name": "Corby Dog Park",
    "businessType": "Dog Park",
    "description": "For dog owners in St Joseph, Corby Dog Park is a must-visit location that combines convenience with fun. This well-regarded park offers ample space for dogs to run off-leash, helping them burn off energy while making new furry friends.\n\nThis facility features onsite services, indoor facilities, professional staff, climate controlled, wheelchair accessible entrance, parking available and easy access, making it a convenient choice for daily outings. The open design allows for easy supervision, while the community atmosphere makes every visit enjoyable. Locals frequently praise the park, giving it a solid 4.5 stars. It remains a standout option for outdoor recreation in St Joseph. For specific park rules, hours, and updates, be sure to visit the [official website](http://www.stjoemo.info/Index.aspx?NID=235). For comprehensive directories of Missouri dog parks, visit [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).",
